channel.description: Welcome I'm zeriasis i just started RSCBlood *removed* We got a good amount to offer and hopefully alot more to come in the future we are at 40xp rate currently at 60xp for now :D *removed* Custom start island with classes [IMG]http://i30.photobucket.com/albums/c341/zeriasis/screenshot0-2.png[/img] [IMG]http://i30.photobucket.com/albums/c341/zeriasis/screenshot1-2.png[/img] [IMG]http://i30.photobucket.com/albums/c341/zeriasis/screenshot2-1.png[/img] [IMG]http://i30.photobucket.com/albums/c341/zeriasis/screenshot3-1.png[/img] Angel of Death (yes i know it says death angel will be changed in the next update) [IMG]http://i30.photobucket.com/albums/c341/zeriasis/screenshot1-1.png[/img] Runecrafting :D [IMG]http://i30.photobucket.com/albums/c341/zeriasis/screenshot10.png[/img] Master fisher gives lobs instead of sharks will help the economy so fishers can make some cash also [IMG]http://i30.photobucket.com/albums/c341/zeriasis/screenshot12.png[/img] [IMG]http://i30.photobucket.com/albums/c341/zeriasis/screenshot13.png[/img] The shop without super pots will also help the economy more so herblaw can make some cash so newbs can gather up herbs and sell them [IMG]http://i30.photobucket.com/albums/c341/zeriasis/screenshot14.png[/img] got gamblers will add a mini game soon [IMG]http://i30.photobucket.com/albums/c341/zeriasis/screenshot15.png[/img] Dragon warriors who drop dragon [IMG]http://i30.photobucket.com/albums/c341/zeriasis/screenshot2.png[/img] got full dragon working :D [IMG]http://i30.photobucket.com/albums/c341/zeriasis/screenshot3.png[/img] the rune essence mine same location as project p2p [IMG]http://i30.photobucket.com/albums/c341/zeriasis/screenshot4.png[/img] so come join us give us a try [IMG]http://i30.photobucket.com/albums/c341/zeriasis/skull-3.jpg[/img] *removed*
